Description:
A ripper opportunity for nesters or investors
Freshly painted & well presented, this 1st floor apartment has an airy, spacious vibe & is desirably orientated to the north. The open-plan living room - with leafy outlook, recessed shelving, timber venetians, & parquetry floor - includes a compact, timber kitchen designed for functionality. Among the extras - mirror-fronted fitted BIRs; intercom entry; carport; & communal laundry (1 on each level of the well maintained block). With Ormond Village & public transport nearby, as well as handy access to Caulfield Uni, recreation & reserves.
Benjamin Dax : 0408 560 790

Description:
Earn up to 539,000 Qantas Points*
This stunning apartment has just recently been complete is 1 of just 15 apartments in this exclusive development in the heart of Ormond.
Apartment 15 comprises 2 bedrooms with built-in robes, master with large ensuite, open plan lounge, dining and kitchen with stone bench tops and stainless steel appliances, main bathroom with shower and bath, large entertaining balcony and European laundry.
Features polished floor boards and down lights throughout, split-system air-conditioning, video intercom car space, storage and lift access.
In an ideal and convenient location close to all amenities, the property is just 100m (approx.) from Ormond Station, walking distance to a range of private and public schools, parks within minutes away and about 10 minutes drive to the beach!
There is also substantial retail strip shopping adjacent to the site along North Rd. including an IGA supermarket, eateries, cafes and fresh produce.
Only 3 remaining don't miss out on this first class investment opportunity.
Call Christian Numa 0409 141 510 or email Christian.numa@amity.com.au
By purchasing this eligible property through Amity Property Group, an accredited real estate agent of LK Property Group, you could earn one Qantas Point per dollar paid on the deposit and the balance of the purchase price*. That means buying this property for $539,000, could earn you 539,000 Qantas Points^! To find out more, visit www.lkproperty.com.au
*Terms and conditions
*You must be a member of the Qantas Frequent Flyer program to earn points. Membership and the earning and redemption of points is subject to the terms and conditions of the Qantas Frequent Flyer program available at qantas.com/terms. Members who purchase an eligible property from an accredited agent of LK Property Group, will earn 1 Qantas Point per dollar paid to the vendor or its representative in respect of the deposit and balance of the purchase price only. No points will be earned on any government taxes and charges paid, including stamp duty. The Property must be purchased through a real estate agent accredited by LK Property Group. A list of accredited agents is available at www.lkproperty.com.au. You must provide your Qantas Frequent Flyer membership number to the accredited agent prior to the payment of the deposit. Points will be allocated to the nominated Qantas Frequent Flyer account(s) in two stages. Stage 1: upon the contract becoming unconditional and full deposit being paid. Stage 2: upon settlement of the Property and the balance of the purchase price being paid. Points will be credited to the Qantas Frequent Flyer account(s) within 6 weeks after payment has been received under each qualifying stage.
^ Points value is based on the purchase of the maximum selling price of a property at 15/494 North Road, Ormond, Vic 3162, being $539,000 and is subject to availability

Description:
Innovative, In-Zone & Accommodating!
Fresh & funky, this brand new townhouse offers 2 courtyards, auto double garage & 4 panel-heated robed bedrooms, surrounded by eclectic angles, neutral earthy tones & even a timber screened private balcony off the upstairs retreat. Say goodbye to boring and hello to warm polished boards, air-conditioned kitchen with stone-topped breakfast bar & a family room offering north & south facing courtyards so you can follow the sunshine! A downstairs bedroom & dual entry bathroom, plus 3 bedrooms & 2nd family bathroom upstairs (master with massive skylit WIR & dual vanity ensuite), complete this well located treasure, moments to Ormond shops, zone 1 station & in-zone McKinnon Secondary & Primary Schools.

Description:
SOLD by Tom Grieve
Love the space and indoor/outdoor feel of this funky 1 bedroom ground floor security apartment.
Styled with stone & marble benchtops, high ceilings and open plan ease, this eye-opening apartment features an entry foyer, open plan living & dining with galley style stone kitchen (Ariston stainless steel appliances including dishwasher) opening to a terracotta verandah and alfresco courtyard, a spacious bedroom with a wall of mirrored BIRs, sleek bathroom and Euro laundry.
A stylish first home or savvy investment, complete with R/C air cond, intercom access and security basement parking with storage cage.
Unbelievably close to North Road shops, cafes, restaurants, the Monash Uni bus and city train, it's lifestyle living at its best in this tranquil tree lined street.

Description:
SOLD by Tom Grieve
A fantastic find, this well maintained 2 bedroom villa is full of warmth and character with the spaciousness you want to be inspired. A neat number, this idyllic starter features an inviting living room with decorative skylight, north facing kitchen with large meals area, 2 double bedrooms (BIRs), tasteful bathroom with separate toilet and laundry with access to the tranquil paved north facing alfresco courtyard. In a small group of three villas, this sought after home is both comfortable as is or ready for some new style, complete with security doors, slate floors, slim line blinds, gas ducted heating, car space and its own carport. Superbly located to all of North Road's cafes, restaurants and convenience shopping, walk to the train, Monash Uni bus and glorious parks.

Description:
Secluded & spacious in the centre of it all
Super sized, perfectly presented and situated just off the strip, this secluded townhouse has all you could want in the centre of it all. Set quietly to the rear within a minute's walk of the strip and station, this private three bedroom, 2.5 bathroom townhouse is the complete package with a large lounge, a tiled dining or casual area around a spacious kitchen and a dedicated first-floor master level starring a vast master bedroom with dual "his and hers" robes and an ensuite. Optioned up with a complete package of prestige extras, there's ducted heating plus reverse-cycle air-conditioning, ducted vacuum, alarm, 2nd & 3rd bedrooms with robes ...even great under-stair and attic storage. Outdoors offers more too with an auto-entry garage (with internal and courtyard access) a carspace in front and a generous courtyard behind. Jump off the train, grab the shopping, be home in a minute - you can have it all in the centre of it all.

Featuring a covered entertaining area overlooking elegant landscaped gardens, gas ducted heating, reverse cycle air conditioner, ducted vacuum, security alarm, single garage/workshop plus double carport, ideally situated close to Ormond station and North Road shopping strip.
